data.description: Welcome to this 4-bedroom, 2-bath home in a prime location! The kitchen, equipped with ample cabinet space, seamlessly opens to the spacious living area. The fourth bedroom offers flexibility as an optional study, catering to your lifestyle needs. The master bedroom features an en-suite bathroom for added privacy. A covered patio overlooks the generous backyard, providing an ideal outdoor retreat. Nestled in a friendly neighborhood with easy access to schools, shopping, and dining, this home blends style and functionality for a perfect living experience. Don't miss out – schedule a showing today! *seller will be replacing carpet in bedroom without carpet*
